<div class="yui-g">
	<div class="section">
		<h3>What is My Tawala?</h3>
		<p>
			The My Tawala page is where a Designer spends most of his time. It is the command center for 
			managing, using, editing and controlling all of your Tawala applications. 
		</p>
		<br />
		<p>
			From this page you can review all of your applications and, by clicking, drill into the detail 
			page for any one.		
		</p>
		<br />
		<p>
			In the detail pages, you can review your client's responses to the applet, send invitations 
			to use it to your clients, wire it into your Web site, revise, purge or delete it and many 
			other management tasks.
		</p>
		<br />
		<p>
			You can also publish your favorite applets to the community library to share with others, 
			keep track of past versions, and export or backup your data. You can change themes and styles, 
			remove old applications or just make them inactive.
		</p>
	</div>
</div>
